graph TD
    A["Application calls CalculatorService divide"] --> B{"Has SafeExecution"}
    B -->|Yes| C[Interceptor Aspect matches target method]
    B -->|No| D[Method executes normally]
    C --> E[Invoke around advice interceptor]
    E --> F[Proceed to method implementation]
    F --> G{"Throws ArithmeticException"}
    G -->|No| H[Return actual result to caller]
    G -->|Yes| I{"SafeExecution annotation present"}
    I -->|Yes| J[Log error details and fallback reason]
    J --> K[Return fallback value]
    I -->|No| L[Log missing annotation error and rethrow]
    L --> M[Exception propagates to caller]
    D --> H
    K --> H
    M --> H
    style H fill:#e0f7fa,stroke:#00796b,stroke-width:2px
    style K fill:#fff9c4,stroke:#f57f17,stroke-width:2px
    style M fill:#ffcdd2,stroke:#b71c1c,stroke-width:2px
